Package de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.api

Class Summary
CriteriaIterable<T> This class represents an Iterable for CriteriaIterator.
CriteriaIterator<T> Universal Iterator that can be used for iteration over any UBY-LMF element.
Uby Uby class represents the main entrance point to the UBY API.
UbyQuickAPI This class represents an extension of the Uby class and offers additional methods for quick searching of different UBY-LMF elements in a database containing a LexicalResource.
UbyStatistics This class represents an extension of the Uby class to support collecting resource statistics.
